snippet.title: Project Winter Cinematic Trailer
snippet.description:
Survive & Escape in this 8 person multiplayer game focusing on social deception and survival. The Survivors goal is to work together, gather resources and escape. Unbeknownst to them, Traitors are within the group whose only goal is to stop them by any means necessary.
